import "./Stacks.css" export default function Stacks() { /* -- Had to add extra lines for touch events -- */ window.onmousedown = (e) => handleOnDown(e); window.ontouchstart = (e) => handleOnDown(e.touches[0]); window.onmouseup = (e) => handleOnUp(e); window.ontouchend = (e) => handleOnUp(e.touches[0]); window.onmousemove = (e) => handleOnMove(e); window.ontouchmove = (e) => handleOnMove(e.touches[0]); return (
); }
